accessibility.text: Ian Tyler Applebaum • Adjunct Instructor • Temple University CIS
Stories should come straight from your requirements document.
You could also go back to your Miro Event Storming board and use the events as possible stories. (there is a miro feature that lets you add these stickies straight into Jira)
Stories could also take the shape:
As a user, I want to ______ so that I can _________
